Line5.103AFA: They have been gone all night... I think it's time I went after him, but the forest is dangerous. Would you accompany me?
Line3.103AFA: I went to confront them, but they fled towards a strange light in the forest.
Line1.103AFA: My husband, Feodor, left our home in the middle of the night. I heard him talking to someone, another woman.
